def sinplot(flip =1):
    x = np.linspace(0,15,100)
    for i in range(1,5):
        plt.plot(x, np.sin(x+i*0.5)*(7-i)*flip)
sns.set_style("white")
sns.set_palette("magma")
sinplot()
